cs.NI, cs.CR, cs.IT, cs.SY, cs.AR. 

The paper discusses the development of an open-source platform for LTE experimentation, which involves aspects of networking (cs.NI), security (cs.CR), information theory (cs.IT), systems and control (cs.SY), and architecture (cs.AR). However, since the focus is on LTE networks and their evolution, cs.NI is the most likely category.
